*puppet-0.24.5-r2 (24 Sep 2008)

  24 Sep 2008; MATSUU Takuto <matsuu@gentoo.org> files/puppet.init,
  files/puppetmaster.init, metadata.xml, +puppet-0.24.5-r2.ebuild:
